  "description": "Compatibility between Better Combat and Lukas' Weapon Leveling",
  "body": "\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KQNWf12.png\" />\n    <br><br>\n</div>\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Loader-Forge%20%7C%20Fabric-ecebe6?labelColor=078200&style=for-the-badge\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Version-1.20.1-ecebe6?labelColor=078200&style=for-the-badge\" />\n  <br>\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Architectury%20API-required-ecebe6?labelColor=fc7200&style=for-the-badge\" />\n</div>\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Server%20side-required-ecebe6?labelColor=078200&style=for-the-badge\" />\n  <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Client%20side-required-ecebe6?labelColor=078200&style=for-the-badge\" />\n  <br>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/AKMkECwnqf\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/973266096763318303?color=7289DA&label=Discord&logo=Discord&style=for-the-badge\" />\n  </a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <br>\n    <font size=\"6\"><b>Level up and Fight Better!</b></font>\n    <br>\n    <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MdjA2H2.png\" width=\"90%\"/>\n</div>\n\n<br>\n<hr>\n<br>\n\n<div align=\"left\">\n    <font size=\"5\"><b>Features</b></font>\n    <br>\n    <br>\n    <font size=\"4\"><b>Dual Wielding</b></font>\n    <br>\n    <font size=\"4\">Dual Wielding Weapons applies XP to the correct weapon used by the player. </font>\n    <br>\n    <br>\n</div>\n<br>\n<div align=\"left\">\n    <font size=\"5\"><b>Why should I use this mod?</b></font>\n    <br>\n    <br>\n    <font size=\"4\">While Weapon Leveling can function with Better Combat on its own, you may want to use it alongside it to level your offhand weapons. This was a feature in older versions of WL, so if you are using WeaponLeveling below 3.0.0, this mod is not needed.</font>\n    <br>\n    <font size=\"4\">The decision to split it into a new mod was made to make Future Updates faster and more streamlined.\n</font>\n    <br>\n    <br>\n</div>\n<br>\n<hr>\n<br>\n<div align=\"center\">\n    <br>\n    <font size=\"4\">This is an official Addon for Weapon Leveling</font>\n    <br>\n    <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/weapon-leveling\">\n      <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Uxu46dk.png\" width=\"90%\"/>\n    </a>\n    <br>\n \n</div>\n\n<br>\n<div align=\"left\">\n    <font size=\"5\"><b>Addon Info</b></font>\n    <br>\n    <font size=\"4\" >This addon is made by GekidoLukas, the creator of Weapon Leveling. All Issues regarding this addon are to be posted on <a href=\"https://github.com/GekidoLukas/wl_bc_compat/issues\">this mod's issue page</a>. Requesting another compatibility addon can be done via <a href=\"https://github.com/GekidoLukas/weaponleveling/issues\">Weapon Leveling's issue page</a></font>\n    <br>\n    <br>\n</div>",
